The directrory 'dataglove' contains a ROS publisher for the 5DT Ultra glove:
http://www.5dt.com/products/pdataglove5u.html

The driver must be installed separatly. 

To start a dataglove node: 
1. Make sure that you hane the right premmistion, e.g.,
   sudo chmod 666 /dev/usb/hiddevX 
   
   where X is the portnumber
2. Modify the port in the launch file, dataglove.launch
3. Run roslaunch:
   roslaunch dataglove dataglove.launch


The directrory 'shadow' contains a ROS publisher for the Shadow Pneumatic Control Unit
http://www.shadowrobot.com/SPCU/overview.shtml


